1. **Čuvar** je bio vrlo ozbiljan dok je obilazio zgradu. (The *guard* was very serious as he patrolled the building.)
2. Moraš poštovati odluke *čuvara* pravila na bazenu. (You have to respect the *lifeguard's* rules at the pool.)
3. Nisam siguran da li je *čuvar* taj koji je vidio lopova sinoć. (I'm not sure if the *watchman* was the one who saw the thief last night.)
4. *Čuvarima* u zoološkom vrtu je potrebno puno strpljenja i ljubavi prema životinjama. (The *keepers* at the zoo need a lot of patience and love for animals.)
5. Naše selo ima starog *čuvara* koji brine o svim stvarima. (Our village has an old *caretaker* who takes care of everything.)
6. *Čuvaru* smo morali pokazati dozvolu za ulazak u zgradu. (We had to show the *guard* our permit to enter the building.)
7. U šumi smo naišli na *čuvare* prirode koji su nas upozorili da ne smijemo paliti vatru. (In the forest, we encountered *nature guardians* who warned us not to start a fire.)
8. Moj otac je bio *čuvar* u tvornici prije nego što se umirovio. (My father was a *watchman* at the factory before he retired.)